			'Birkholz is a German brand founded in 2017. "We are a family-run perfume manufacturer from Berlin. With our Birkholz Perfume Manufacture brand, we have made it our mission to provide our customers with time and attention to detail. The scent of a freshly picked rose, a potpourri of different spices, the interplay of different fragrance compositions - we have invested a lot of time in the selection of the most precious perfume oils. And we traveled around the world to get inspiration from putting together the notes.\nAs perfume sommeliers, we know how important the right fragrance can be. This not only emphasizes moments and makes them something special, but is also part of your own personality. Every perfume should therefore be as individual as its wearer. We want our customers to experience this individualization.\nOur exquisite perfumes, as well as the selection of the bottles we created, caps with handmade leather in different colors and our own dedications are therefore available in the perfume factory and in the online shop. Each perfume thus has its own meaning and tells the very individual story of the wearer.\nWe make buying perfume a valuable experience again and stand by our guests as experienced fragrance consultants at every step of the creation." - a note from the brand.\nDesigner Birkholz has 33 perfumes in our fragrance base. Birkholz is a new fragrance brand. The earliest edition was created in 2017 and the newest is from 2020.',
