			"Human body is totally pervaded by a liquid vital rush that brings us what we more are fond of: life. Filled with legends and meanings,‚ blood is soaked with mistery,‚ fascination and respect: it’s the most tested and studied part of human body. Hiding the multitude of secrets that reveals our inner and unique way of being.\nBLOOD CONCEPT is a ceremony devoted to the pulse of life and its visceral boost. It is actually the river of life.\nOur four fragrances, A, B, AB, 0, retrace the evolution of manhood through time and its record of information, history and mutation, so well kept in the vital flushing of blood.\nBLOOD CONCEPT is a mystic ritual with no flowers to be found: deep as primeval Africa in 0‚ aromatic as the scent of familiar land in A, bold as unpredictable itineraries in B, sharp and freezing as a metropolitan skyline in AB.\nEnding each time with the same subtle and mysterious note:the metallic vague suspicion of blood.\nDesigner Blood Concept has 22 perfumes in our fragrance base. Blood Concept is a new fragrance brand. The earliest edition was created in 2011 and the newest is from 2016. Blood Concept fragrances were made in collaboration with perfumers Antoine Lie, Celine Ripert, Philippe Bousseton, Christian Vermorel and Cyrill Rolland.",
