		description:
			'"Filippo Sorcinelli is a lifestyle brand, the result of a collaboration between the arts. In 2014, as a tribute to the Atelier LAVS, the first fragrance of the UNUM collection was born, like a sort of olfactory tailoring, then followed by perfumes dedicated to the artistic passions\nof their creator: gothic art, music, photography ... the fog. Filippo Sorcinelli is not only synonymous with niche fragrances; the company\'s projects range volcanically in every sector: art, events, fashion, design, in a concept of lifestyle that embraces different aspects of contemporary times through unusual shapes and materials. A journey through spirituality and harmony, in the constant and audacious search for beauty." (A note from the brand.)\nDesigner Filippo Sorcinelli has 17 perfumes in our fragrance base. Filippo Sorcinelli is a new fragrance brand. The earliest edition was created in 2014 and the newest is from 2019.',
