			'Abdes Salaam Attar, previously known as La Via Del Profumo, is an Italian niche perfume brand founded by Dominique Durbana. "Dominique Dubrana was born in France, and traveled to Africa, the Middle East, Afghanistan and Pakistan. His travels led him down a new spiritual path and he became a Sufi. Eventually he moved to Italy and there began practicing the art of perfumery. He quickly focused on natural ingredients as an aesthetic choice, for their healing properties and in an effort to create fragrances using the best materials available.\nKnown as Abdes Salaam Attar, Dubrana began composing and selling his perfumes in Italy in 1988. In 1999, he opened his website, profumo.it, to offer his all-natural "Scents of the Soul” to perfume lovers around the world." - a note from the brand.\nDesigner Abdes Salaam Attars Perfumes has 41 perfumes in our fragrance base. Abdes Salaam Attars Perfumes is a new fragrance brand. The earliest edition was created in 2010 and the newest is from 2016. The nose who worked on the fragrances is Dominique Dubrana.',
