		title: "AbdesSalaam Attar Perfumes",
		description:
			'AbdesSalaam Attar Perfumes offers fragrances which are handcrafted with the best aromatic raw material and are certified 100% natural. Besides perfumes, the brand also offers aromatherapy products for the home and body, as well as pure perfume attars and didactical kits.\nThe perfumer states, "I chose to make natural perfumes as someone chooses to work with precious metals and rare gemstones instead of plastic beads and pearls of colored glass. The first reason has been that at the beginning of my perfumer’s life, I experienced severe allergies with some synthetic raw materials. The second reason is that I always wanted the real thing at any cost, and in the world of perfumery the real simply means the natural. There has been no ideology in my choice, only discovering the truth."',
