			"Compagnia Delle Indie is an Italian company founded in 1598. It is famous for its themed collections inspired by sunshine, sea and vacation. The latest collection is very interesting, being dedicated to the continents of the world. This fragrant journey is illustrated by different colors, dynamics and natural beauty that evoke mysteries from around the world, attracting and seducing with the magic of specific aromas.\nThe collection The Continents contains five fragrances named after the continents: Oceania Tiare Blossom (Flor di Tiare), Africa Desert Tobacco, Asia Ginger Dust (Polvere di Zenzero), Europe Mediterranean Breeze (Brezza Mediterranea), Le Americhe Caribbean Fruits.\nThis line is designed to actuate olfactive dreamy voyages around the world, emphasizing the precious essences of each continent. The graphics and the motif on the bottles show a part of each continent separately, while the warm amber colors on the 100 ml bottles give an exotic effect to the composition.\nOceania Tiare Blossom emphasizes the Tiare flower, which is the symbol of Polynesia, displaying the spirit and the heat of its residents as well as the joy of life. This fragrance opens with Tiare flower, orchid and peach, followed by the heart of peony, freesia, orange blossom and lotus, ending at the base of musk, vanilla and sandalwood.\nAfrica Desert Tobacco is dedicated to the magical herb tobacco that has been used from ancient times in the making of massage oils to stimulate local circulations and relax muscle tensions. The perfume opens with notes of bergamot and mandarin. The heart is filled with gorse berries, nutmeg and incense, while the base consists of patchouli, vanilla and tobacco.\nAsia Ginger Dust (Polvere di Zenzero) emphasizes ginger as the attributive aroma of the Far East. Ginger captures with its lemony–woody aroma, similar to lemon and coriander, with some dense and sweet nuances. The fragrance is opened with citrus explosion of bergamot, lemon, lime, grapefruit and orange, followed by the heart of ginger, clove, cardamom and heliotrope. Accords of musk form the base.\nEurope Mediterranean Breeze brings a Mediterranean feeling of winds that tickle and relax with its fresh marine aromas. This is a fragrance strongly and vibrantly connected with the richness of natural aromas, provoking an olfective escape to the place we dream of. It opens with aromas of marine air, grapefruit and star anis. The heart is composed of white rose, lily-of-the-valley and light flowers, while the base is formed of see algae and white musk.\nLe Americhe Caribbean Fruits reflects the sun above the water; a warm breeze that causes feelings to overwhelm like a sea weaves. A cocktail of exotic fruit, a true delight for all the senses, represents the fragrance Le Americhe Caribbean Fruits. Top notes are red berries, raspberry, papaya, mango and cranberry. The heart is filed with aloe vera, palm milk and lily-of-the-valley, while the base consists of woody notes, white musk, sandalwood and amber.\nDesigner Compagnia Delle Indie has 21 perfumes in our fragrance base. The earliest edition was created in 2000 and the newest is from 2013.",
