		description:
			"Sergio Scaglietti is an Italian niche brand founded by Matteo and Simone Scaglietti in 2017.\n\"Sergio Scaglietti, world renowned car designer and ‘carrozziere’ from Modena, was one of Enzo Ferrari’s closest friends and confidant. Talented Sergio had the incredible ability to shape metal with his hands and creativity producing some of the most beautiful and sought-after cars in the world: the famous Ferrari Testarossa, the legendary Ferrari 250 GTO and the iconic Ferrari 250 California. Sergio inventiveness and craftsmanship now shine through Simone, one of his grandchildren, who, after working for the family beauty products business, has today created four unique fragrances inspired by the stunningly beautiful cars designed by his grandfather at the celebrated Scaglietti Carrozzeria. The ‘Racing Line’ range takes inspiration from the elements that have characterized Sergio's world famous car production. The harmonious curves and smooth edges, that he so loved, are replicated in the simple and elegant silhouette of the perfume bottle sealed by a steel cap which recalls wheel bolts. The outer packaging features a reusable and recyclable aluminium tin, using the same material that the Carrozzeria would have utilised to create new and exciting prototypes, whilst its shape is inspired by the pots of paint supplied with every Scaglietti model, as the colour of each car was tailor-made. Sergio was also one of the first car designers to employ laser serigraphy, a technology that Simone has now chosen to use for the engravings on his refined packaging.\n ‘Tradition and Innovation’ this was Sergio's motto.\nDare with new shapes, but never lose sense of what you are doing, where you are coming from and what you wish to create. This is the concept which transpires from the simple and innovative packaging; effectively elegant yet firmly focusing our attention on the true nature of Simone’s project and passion: his fragrances. With the Scaglietti ‘Racing Line’ Simone has created a unique range of perfumes produced with the best raw materials expertly blended to achieve complex olfactory pyramids and engaging bouquets, which will always make you stand out from the crowd like his grandfather iconic cars do.\" - a note from the brand.\nSergio Scaglietti is a new fragrance brand. Designer Sergio Scaglietti has 4 perfumes in our fragrance base all launched in 2017. The nose who worked on the fragrances is Simone Scaglietti.",
