		description:
			'Ganache Parfums takes gourmand fragrances seriously and they are unapologetically gourmand and proud. The brand was founded in 2016 by perfumer Jarekhye Covarrubias, who observed in his 20 plus years as a perfumer and fragrance aficionado that nothing can spark fond memories and create powerful connections faster than a good gourmand fragrance. Covarrubias notes, "I am always in awe of how the pleasantly sweet aroma of a gourmand fragrance can create an atmosphere of comfort and instantly become a conversation starter." Armed with this knowledge, he set out to create a company focused on offering high quality gourmand perfumes that are complex enough to be sumptuously and decadently delicious works of art and yet still simple enough to combined with other fragrances in the house to create new and unique confectionery gourmand creations. All Ganache Parfums fragrances are handmade in small batches using time tested artisan techniques at their studio in Berkeley, California.\nDesigner Ganache Parfums has 65 perfumes in our fragrance base. Ganache Parfums is a new fragrance brand. The earliest edition was created in 2017 and the newest is from 2019. The nose who worked on the fragrances is Jarekhye Covarrubias.',
