			"Sebastian Signs is an American fragrance house based in Los Angeles, CA. Founded on the philosophy that luxury should be an essential part of everyone's life, Sebastian Signs combines founder and perfumer Sherri Sebastian's passions for fragrance, design and composition. Originally a chemist by training, Sherri Sebastian began her career in a flavor house in Brooklyn before studying perfumery alongside a master perfumer in Manhattan. Her 20-year career as a perfumer included fragrances created for major cosmetics companies and designers before she founded Sebastian Signs in 2003.\nSebastian Signs offers botanically based fragrances via the Purusa® Naturals collection as well as fragrances composed in both classic and modern styles with the Numbers collection.\nSebastian Signs is a new fragrance brand. Designer Sebastian Signs has 7 perfumes in our fragrance base all launched in 2013. The nose who worked on the fragrances is Sherri Sebastian.",
