			'Vanessa Somerset Design is a natural perfumery and design business based in Harrisburg, Pennsylvania in the United States. Vanessa Somerset is a registered nurse with a "slight obsession for all things botanical and beautiful." She began exploring aromatherapy and crafting aromatic body products at age 19, eventually launching a botanical-based business called Sevansa Spa. Vanessa discovered her love of photography while photographing her spa product line. The product line was refocused as Vanessa Somerset Design in 2015, which unites Vanessa\'s two passions—natural perfumery and photography—with her love of botany as a common thread between the two.\nFrom Vanessa Somerset: "Vanessa Somerset Design is a beautiful expression of the things that I love and want to share with you as I strive to uniquely interpret the botanical world through scent and sight. It’s a reminder to literally stop and smell the roses. I carefully create my handmade natural perfume oils with 100% natural essential oils and plant extracts, while my fine art photography captures nature and your most precious moments through a refreshingly colorful perspective. I truly believe that nature is God\'s handiwork shining beautifully for us to enjoy, and Vanessa Somerset Design is a celebration of this. I hope that every fine art photograph and perfume that you discover here enhances your life the way that they\'ve enhanced mine."\nVanessa Somerset Design is a new fragrance brand. Designer Vanessa Somerset Design has 3 perfumes in our fragrance base all launched in 2015. The nose who worked on the fragrances is Vanessa Somerset.',
