			'Nakuna Helsinki founded in Finland, is a new wave Nordic luxury perfume brand with a strong Nordic visual identity. Nakuna Helsinki is founded by a couple Anu Igoni and Jaakko Veijola, who both are entrepreneurs and creative directors working in design and marketing.\nNakuna Helsinki launches in 2020 with 5 perfumes, developed in collaboration with the world’s leading perfumers (Yann Vassnier, Nadège Legarlantezec, Fernandez Jorge and Olivier Pescheux) by Givaudan.\n"Our dear country Finland. One can drink straight from the stream, eat wild berries from backyard and leave doors unlocked. For a couple of months we have lights fully on 24h until they are switched of for months.\nTo endure the darkness, coldness and everything being so ok, we need our escapes. We have our summercabins and islands. We travel to feel dirt, noise and chaos, since that’s life. We explore scents, tastes and colours of south, and bring them back home to endure the bleak winter months. We dream, imagine and create. We love it here and dream to be somewhere else. This is what Nakuna Helsinki is all about." - a note from the brand.\nNakuna Helsinki is a new fragrance brand. Designer Nakuna Helsinki has 5 perfumes in our fragrance base all launched in 2020. Nakuna Helsinki fragrances were made in collaboration with perfumers Olivier Pescheux, Yann Vasnier, Nadege le Garlantezec and Jordi Fernandez.',
